<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-14503] camel-package-maven-plugin:generate fails with NPE for component outside the camel source tree</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-14503</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The mojo camel-package-maven-plugin:generate assumes that components are all belonging to the camel source tree so when it is applied to external components, it fails with NPE here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/master/tooling/maven/camel-package-maven-plugin/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/maven/packaging/EndpointSchemaGeneratorMojo.java#L1230-L1231&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/master/tooling/maven/camel-package-maven-plugin/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/maven/packaging/EndpointSchemaGeneratorMojo.java#L1230-L1231&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13283575">CAMEL-14503</key>
            <summary>camel-package-maven-plugin:generate fails with NPE for component outside the camel source tree</summary>
